<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> بابُ صَيْدِ الْمِعْرَاضِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ ابْنُ عُمَرَ فِي الْمَقْتُولَةِ بِالْبُنْدُقَةِ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تِلْكَ الْمَوْقُوذَةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَكَرِهَهُ سَالِمٌ وَالْقَاسِمُ وَمُجَاهِدٌ وَإِبْرَاهِيمُ وَعَطَاءٌ وَالْحَسَنُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَكَرِهَ الْحَسَنُ رَمْيَ الْبُنْدُقَةِ فِي الْقُرَى وَالأَمْصَارِ، وَلَا يَرَى بَأسًا فِيمَا سِوَاهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>